== Abrabɔ ahyɛaseɛ ==
Yɔ wo Francis wɔ Kotonima bosome da a ɛtɔ so eduonu baako (21) wɔ afe 1959 mu wɔ Bono Ahafo Mamtamu wɔ Gana. Ɔnyaa abɔdin krataa ( Bachelor of Arts) wɔ Sociology ne Geography fri Kwame Nkrumah Suapɔn ma abɔdemu nyansapɛ ne abɛfo. Ɔyɛ adwuma sɛ sociologyini ansa ɔrekɔ amanyɔsem mu.

== Amanyɔ adwuma ==
Francis hyɛ ne amanyɔ akwantuo wɔ Ɔpɛpɔn da a ɛtɔ so nsɔn wɔ afe edunkron ne eduokron miensa mu (1993) wɔ abre a ɔdi nkunim wɔ [[1992 Ghana Mmarahyɛ badwa abatoɔ|1992 Gana mmarahyɛbadwam abatoɔ]]  a ɛkɔ so Ɔpɛnimma bosome no da a ɛtɔ so eduonu nkron (29) wɔ afe 1992 mu.

Wɔ san to aba ma no kɔɔ mmarhyɛbadwam a ɛtɔ so mienu wɔ kwasafoman a ɛtɔ so anan wɔ Gana abre a odi  nkunim wɔ [[1996 Ghanaian Abatoɔ|1996 Gana abatoɔ no mu]]. Ɔdi nkunim wɔ Emmanuel Kuffuor a ɔgyena ma amanyɔkuo NPP ne Yaw Ohene Manu a ɔgyena ma National Independence Party so. Ɔnyaa mba no mu  42.90% wɔ mba a wɔ to yɛ no nyinaa mu wɔ abre a amanyɔkuo NDC anemsini no ne NIP anemsini no nyaa 20.80% ne 10.60%. Ɔhyere na akonnwa no abre a George William Amponsah a ɔwɔ amanyɔ kuo [[NPP|New Patriotic Party]] mu no di ne so nkunim wɔ afe [[2000 Ghana abatoo|2000 Gana abatoɔ mu no]].

